1
00:00:27,566 --> 00:00:28,866
That's enough, Wian.

2
00:00:30,033 --> 00:00:30,733
Why?!

3
00:00:31,033 --> 00:00:32,753
I think we should not go further than this.

4
00:00:33,766 --> 00:00:35,433
Let's not cross any more line.

5
00:00:37,233 --> 00:00:39,300
If one day,
Chok do something like this to me,

6
00:00:40,166 --> 00:00:42,833
I would see sad also.

7
00:00:42,833 --> 00:00:44,000
