8
00:00:51,566 --> 00:00:54,300
I know you're good man. I can feel it.

9
00:00:55,566 --> 00:00:58,133
Please be a good friend of mine.

10
00:00:58,933 --> 00:00:59,933
I'm sorry.

11
00:01:00,633 --> 00:01:01,633
Narin!

12
00:01:02,266 --> 00:01:03,333
I love you!

13
00:01:05,199 --> 00:01:06,199
Narin!

14
00:01:36,300 --> 00:01:37,300
I don't love you.

15
00:01:37,433 --> 00:01:39,033
Get out of my life!
